      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's an interesting way to put it. You mentioned it's more \"inclusive\" now, but I've heard a lot of people online and in the news saying that these changes are actually just making classrooms too political or biased. Do you think those critics have a point, or are they just stuck in the old ways of doing things?",
